snippet.title: Best VGM 2337 - Kirby & The Rainbow Curse - The Final Battle (vs Dark Crafter)
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 1734 - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QN1wbetaaTk
Best VGM 1964 - https://youtu.be/cZVRDjJUPIQ

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Wii U
Kirby & The Rainbow Curse (2015)
The Final Battle (vs Dark Crafter)
Shogo Sakai
